"<command>ark</command> <option>-b</option> <option>-d</option> "
"<replaceable>archiwum.tar.bz2</replaceable> <replaceable>archiwum2.zip</"
"replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-ark.1.docbook:215
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Will first show an extraction options dialog and then extract both "
"<replaceable>archive.tar.bz2</replaceable> and <replaceable>archive2.zip</"
"replaceable> into the directory chosen in the dialog."
msgstr ""
"Wyświetli okno dialogowe opcji rozpakowywania, następnie wypakuje "
"<replaceable>archiwum.tar.bz2</replaceable> i <replaceable>archiwum2.zip</"
"replaceable> do katalogu wybranego w tym oknie."

#. Tag: userinput
#: man-ark.1.docbook:222
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>ark</command> <option>--add-to</option> <replaceable>my-archive."
"zip</replaceable> <replaceable>photo1.jpg</replaceable> <replaceable>text."
"txt</replaceable>"
msgstr ""
"<command>ark</command> <option>--add-to</option> <replaceable>moje-archiwum."
"zip</replaceable> <replaceable>fotografia1.jpg</replaceable> "
"<replaceable>tekst.txt</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-ark.1.docbook:226
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Will create <replaceable>my-archive.zip</replaceable> if does not exist and "
"then add <replaceable>photo1.jpg</replaceable> and <replaceable>text.txt</"
"replaceable> to it."
msgstr ""
"Utworzy <replaceable>moje-archiwum.zip</replaceable>, o ile takie nie "
"istnieje oraz doda <replaceable>fotografię1.jpg</replaceable> i "
"<replaceable>tekst.txt</replaceable> do niego."

